item.title: Ai
item.description: write this more formally: Regarding the previous work, the first time I started vmware installation it asked me for the license. Then I closed the VMware installation and ran the command that adds the license (/usr/lib/vmware/bin/vmware-vmx-debug –new-sn ZZ352-2UZDQ-48EUZ-9WW7Z-WCKYD) I re-ran VMware and VMWare stopped asking for the license so it worked, the last command I always throw segmenetation fault fails and it is a useless (/usr/lib/vmware/bin/v mware-enter-serial) anyway the installation was done correctly.
